TITLE: Loading MAUI Assets Using FileSystem API
DESCRIPTION: C# async method demonstrating how to access raw assets bundled with the application using the FileSystem.OpenAppPackageFileAsync method. The example shows how to open a file and read its contents using a StreamReader.
SOURCE: https://github.com/packtpublishing/.net-maui-cookbook.git/blob/main/Chapter08/c8-AsyncLoading/c8-AsyncLoading/Resources/Raw/AboutAssets.txt#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: csharp
CODE:
```
async Task LoadMauiAsset()
{
	using var stream = await FileSystem.OpenAppPackageFileAsync("AboutAssets.txt");
	using var reader = new StreamReader(stream);

	var contents = reader.ReadToEnd();
}
```

